<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c1">" مجهول"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٧٦)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
